data.title: Nazr Mohammed Player Profile, Oklahoma City Thunder
data.meta_description: Get the latest news, stats and more about Nazr Mohammed on RealGM.com
data.text: Jun 24, 1998 - The Utah Jazz selected Nazr Mohammed in Round 1 with Pick 29 in the 1998 NBA Draft. Jun 24, 1998 - The Philadelphia Sixers acquired the Draft Rights to Nazr Mohammed from the Utah Jazz in a trade. Jan 21, 1999 - Nazr Mohammed signed a multi-year contract with the Philadelphia Sixers. Feb 22, 2001 - Nazr Mohammed was acquired by the Atlanta Hawks, along with Toni Kukoc, Theo Ratliff, Pepe Sanchez and a TPE, from the Philadelphia Sixers in exchange for Roshown McLeod and Dikembe Mutombo. Jul 1, 2001 - Nazr Mohammed, previously with the Atlanta Hawks, became a free agent. Jul 19, 2001 - Nazr Mohammed signed a multi-year contract with the Atlanta Hawks. Feb 15, 2004 - Nazr Mohammed was acquired by the New York Knicks, along with Tim Thomas, from the Atlanta Hawks in exchange for Michael Doleac, Keith Van Horn and a More Favorable 2005 2nd round pick. Feb 24, 2005 - Nazr Mohammed was acquired by the San Antonio Spurs, along with Jamison Brewer and a TPE, from the New York Knicks in exchange for Malik Rose, a conditional 2004 1st round pick (PHX own) and a conditional 2006 1st round pick (SAN own). Jul 1, 2006 - Nazr Mohammed, previously with the San Antonio Spurs, became a free agent. Jul 18, 2006 - Nazr Mohammed signed a multi-year contract with the Detroit Pistons. Dec 14, 2007 - Nazr Mohammed was acquired by the Charlotte Hornets from the Detroit Pistons in exchange for Primoz Brezec and Walter Herrmann. Feb 24, 2011 - Nazr Mohammed was acquired by the Oklahoma City Thunder from the Charlotte Hornets in exchange for Morris Peterson and D.J. White. Jun 28, 2011 - Nazr Mohammed signed a veteran extension with the Oklahoma City Thunder. Jul 1, 2012 - Nazr Mohammed, previously with the Oklahoma City Thunder, became a free agent. Jul 26, 2012 - Nazr Mohammed signed a contract with the Chicago Bulls. Jul 1, 2013 - Nazr Mohammed, previously with the Chicago Bulls, became a free agent. Jul 10, 2013 - Nazr Mohammed signed a contract with the Chicago Bulls. Jul 1, 2014 - Nazr Mohammed, previously with the Chicago Bulls, became a free agent. Jul 17, 2014 - The Chicago Bulls renounced their free-agent exception rights to Nazr Mohammed. Sep 22, 2014 - Nazr Mohammed signed a contract with the Chicago Bulls. Jul 1, 2015 - Nazr Mohammed, previously with the Chicago Bulls, became a free agent. Mar 5, 2016 - Nazr Mohammed signed a contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder. Jul 1, 2016 - Nazr Mohammed, previously with the Oklahoma City Thunder, became a free agent.
